T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"李+x 笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/11592460249/1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F11592460249%2F1000&h=99c6d5d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nX哥: 啲科學家都戇QQ既"},{"pid":"b6b3548f6a464246b91be34ad9e68b3c5059cdbd","tid":2512754,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"有咩咁值得研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n50歲退得休，代表佢好有錢啦，生活質素又好<br />\n越遲退休代表越有生活負擔，早死好正常啫<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果冇錢，俾你長命都係折墮<br />\n<br />\n所以冇錢早死 有錢遲死<br />\n對大家都好.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195fd3cbf7c742a674438f12efd0ab64a8299d96","tid":2512754,"uid":194008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:22:33.000Z","msg":"有錢 -&gt; 早退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窮人 -&gt; 做多幾年嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢人有能力得到好啲醫療服務 所以遲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}